    title: 'Zenka Loan App - Kenya',
    description:
      "Zenka is the most flexible personal loan platform on the market, giving Kenyans more control over their finances with its unique features. We offer a simple registration and application process, after which you will receive your loan straight to your M-Pesa account.\r\n\r\nMoney on your account in just 5 minutes!\r\n\r\nWhat are my loan terms?\r\n\r\nCustomers can express a preference for loans of 61 days.\r\n- 61-day loan payment terms have a one-time processing fee of 9-29%*\r\n- Processing Fee: Range from KSh 45 - KSh 870 for a one-time charge.\r\n- Loan Amount: from KSh 500 to KSh 30,000.\r\n- Grow with Zenka and build your limit up to KSh 30,000 by making your loan repayments on time\r\n\r\nFor example, for a 61-day loan with a principal amount of KSh 1,000, the processing fee would be KSh290 and the total amount due would be KSh 1,290.\r\n\r\nCustomers have the option to repay their loan amounts even up to 12 months (ZenkaFlexi option).\r\n\r\nHave questions? Visit www.zenka.co.ke to check out our FAQs\r\nReady to get started? Download the Zenka app and apply for a loan today.\r\n\r\nPrivacy and permissions: When you download Zenka, we will ask to scan your M-Pesa SMS and other information in order to verify your identity, creditworthiness, and provide you with the fastest loan in Kenya. We take privacy very seriously, and your personal information will never be shared without your direct permission.\r\n\r\nTerms and Conditions: Zenka charges a one-time processing fee of 9-29%* of the principal amount. There is no minimum payment period for repayment; customers may make payments towards their principal at any time following disbursement. Additional terms and conditions apply.\r\nEffective APR: 70.7%-224.89%. Zenka is totally transparent with the fees applied.\r\n\r\nHow does it work?\r\n\r\n1. Download Zenka App\r\nVisit the Google Play Store. Search for Zenka Loan App and download it on your mobile.\r\n\r\n2. Fill the short application form\r\nAfter downloading our app, choose how much money you need and sign up with Zenka.\r\n\r\n3. Receive money on your M-Pesa account\r\nYour application will be evaluated, and when it is approved, you will receive money on your M-Pesa account.\r\n\r\n4. Need additional financing?\r\nMake use of our flexible additional amount feature that allows you to top up your existing loan with extra cash, up to your current credit limit.\r\n\r\n5. Need more time to repay?\r\nLoan extensions give you more control over your loan by letting you postpone your due date by 7, 14 or 30 days.\r\n\r\n6. Repay on time and build a positive credit history\r\nTimely repayment increases your credit limit and allows you to apply for higher amounts in the future.\r\n\r\n\r\nWhat's so special about us?\r\nAdditional amount and extensions do the job!\r\n\r\n- Considering additional financing? Don't miss on great opportunities and top up your existing loan with just a few clicks!\r\n- Need more time to repay? Get control over the unexpected by extending your due date. Enjoy the flexibility we offer.\r\n- Achieve financial harmony! Realize your ideas and needs with our instant personal loans.\r\n\r\n\r\nContact information:\r\n\r\nCall center: + 254 020 765 0878\r\nEmail: support@zenka.co.ke\r\n\r\nZenka Finance Limited\r\nMirage Tower 2, 12th floor, \r\nP.O. BOX 29107-00100\r\nNairobi\r\nKenya",
