    title: 'Senti',
    description:
      'Senti is a micro-credit mobile app that makes it easy for people in Kenya to access a loan, anytime, anywhere. \r\n\r\nHow to Register on Senti\r\n\r\n\u2022 Download the Senti app\r\n\u2022 Register your correct details on the Senti mobile app \r\n\u2022 Verify your details with the One time password sent to you\r\n\u2022 Apply for a loan and get fast cash sent directly to your M-Pesa\r\n\r\nDo you know of our Friendly Loan terms?\r\n\r\n\u2022Up to 90-day loan product. We have options that let you choose what\u2019s right for you as a customer\r\n\u2022 Up to 90 day loan product with repayment terms of a one-time between 15% and 20%\r\n\u2022 Grow with Senti and build your limit up to KSh 70,000 by making your repayments in good time\r\n\r\nHow do I repay my loan?\r\n\r\n\u2022 Repay your loan through the App by Clicking Pay loan and enter your M-pesa Pin on the M-pesa tool kit that will appear on your screen or through our Paybill 517910 enter your phone number as the account number and the amount that is due on the amount section.\r\n\u2022 You can pay in full or make partial payments, anytime on or before your due date\r\n\r\nGain more with Senti in-app features:\r\n\r\n\u2022 You can Buy Airtime straight from your Senti App\r\n\u2022 You can now Lipa Stima or your water Bill with your Senti Loan\r\n\u2022 Track your income vs your spending with our wealth management feature\r\n\u2022 Share Senti with your friends and family to help them sort their Financial Emergencies\r\n\r\n\r\nHave questions? Visit www.Senti.co.ke to check out our FAQs or call 0712517910\r\nReady to get started? Download the Senti app and apply for a loan today.\r\n\r\nTerms and Conditions:\r\n Senti charges a one-time service fee of 10-15%* of principal with a minimum repayment period of 60 days and maximum period of 90 days. There is no minimum payment period for repayment; customers may make payments towards their principal at any time following disbursement. The maximum repayment period for a Senti loan is up to 90 days from disbursement. A one-time extension fee of 7.5% of principal and interest may be applied to loans past due. No other fees will be charged after this time. Additional terms and conditions apply. \r\n\r\n*Effective APR: 90.17-192.5%. Senti does not charge you more than the amount of your due amount which is inclusive of (a one-time extension fee if one pays past our due date that includes a 7-day grace period). We do not compound  \r\n\r\n**A Demonstrative example: KES 40,000.00 loan taken for 90 days may incur a service fee of 15%, for a total cost of KES 46,000.00 if repaid before or on the due date.',
