    title: 'FairMoney: Instant loan app, bill payment and more',
    description:
      "FairMoney is much more than a loan app: not only can you get fast loans but also renew your cable TV subscriptions & recharge airtime and data with a -10% discount and no transaction fees!\r\n\r\nNow loans up to \u20a6500,000!\r\n\r\nLOANS:\r\nInstant loans up \u20a6500,000 without collateral or paperwork.\r\nIf you need money for your business or a personal loan, download the FairMoney app, sign up and follow a simple application process to get an instant loan in only 5 minutes.\r\n\r\nFairMoney is a fast, secure, reliable and free Android mobile banking app, available in Nigeria. We make getting loans and paying bills fast and easy. You can also earn bonus cash when you invite your friends.\r\n\r\nLOAN INSTALMENTS AND INTEREST RATE:\r\nOn FairMoney anyone can access between \u20a61,500 to \u20a6500,000 in loan amount with repayment periods from 60 days and above.\r\n\r\nMonthly interest rates range from 10% to 30% and respective APRs from 120% to 360%.\r\n\r\nWe are giving up to 1% daily discounts to reward our clients for early re-payments and charge up to 1.5% daily late fees for late payments.\r\n\r\nThere are no additional fees for processing your loan or any hidden costs associated.\r\n\r\nYou can repay your loan via bank transfer with your unique Providus Bank account number, USSD or debit card.\r\n\r\nAN EXAMPLE OF A FAIRMONEY LOAN:\r\nBorrow NGN100,000 over 3 months\r\nInterest rate: 30%\r\nThree repayments of NGN 43,333\r\nTotal amount payable: NGN130,000\r\nRepresentative: 120% APR\r\n\r\nBILL PAYMENTS:\r\nFairMoney offers discounts on online payments!\r\nNow you can renew your subscription on DStv, GOtv and Startimes with NO TRANSACTION FEES! \r\nYou can also get a -10% discount instantly when you buy airtime and mobile data on all networks in Nigeria (MTN, Airtel, 9Mobile and Glo).\r\n\r\nAnyone in Nigeria can renew cable TV subscriptions and recharge airtime and data to increase your credit score and get higher loans and discounts.\r\n\r\nFor more information keep reading below or read our Frequently Asked Questions (FAQs) on www.fairmoney.ng. You can also send us an email to help@fairmoney.ng or call our Customer Service Hotline on 01 631 6097 from 9am-5pm every Mon-Fri.\r\n\r\nWHY CHOOSE FAIRMONEY?\r\nWe are more than a loan app.\r\n\r\nNeed a business or personal loan, or a quick and easy way to pay bills? FairMoney is the answer!\r\nWe are working hard to provide you with the best services to make your life better. Very soon you will look to FairMoney for your electricity bill payments, current account, savings and much more!\r\n\r\n- All you need is your phone number and BVN to apply for a loan of up to \u20a6500,000 from your phone.\r\n\r\n- You will receive your loan in only 5 minutes!\r\n\r\n- Spread repayments in multiple instalments for more flexibility and ease.\r\n\r\n- We encrypt the data you choose to share with us to protect your privacy.\r\n\r\n- Get an instant loan or make payments with no hidden charges or transaction fees.\r\n\r\n- Build your credit score and get access to higher loans, discounts or flexible interest rates when repayments are made on time.\r\n\r\n- Track your loan history and transactions to stay on top of your finances.\r\n\r\n- We reward you with a N500 discount off your loan when you invite your friends to get a loan with FairMoney.\r\n\r\n- Get a 10% discount when you buy airtime or mobile data and pay no transaction fees when you renew your cable TV. The cheapest rate in Nigeria!\r\n\r\nHOW TO SIGN UP:\r\n- Download the FairMoney app\r\n- Sign up with your phone number\r\n- Create your secure PIN\r\n\r\nHOW TO APPLY FOR A LOAN:\r\n- Click \u2018Apply\u2019 on the home page\r\n- Answer a few simple questions\r\n- Receive a loan offer\r\n- Select amount and period\r\n- Accept loan offer\r\n- Enter bank details to receive your money\r\n\r\nHOW TO PAY BILLS:\r\n- Select 'Airtime, bills' from the main menu\r\n- Select a category ('Airtime', 'Data' or 'Cable TV')\r\n- Follow the on-screen instructions\r\n- Choose a card\r\n- Confirm payment\r\n\r\nFOR MORE INFORMATION, COMMENTS OR SUGGESTIONS:\r\nSend us an email at help@fairmoney.ng or call our Customer Service Hotline on 01 631 6097 from 9am-5pm every Mon-Fri.",
